<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.4.10">
<l>piṟaicēr nutalār pēṇutal nammaiyi lātamuṉ</l>
<l>naṟaicēr poḻilcūḻ naṟaiyūr toḻuṉeñca mēyeṉṟa</l>
<l>kaṟaiyār neṭuvēl maṅkaiyar kōṉkali kaṉṟicol</l>
<l>maṟavā turaippavar  vāṉavark kiṉṉara cāvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They will become kind kings to the celestials, those who say without lapse,</l>
<l>The words of Kalikaṉṟi, the people of Maṅkai’s king</l>
<l rend="indent">with a blood-covered, long spear,</l>
<l>Who said, “Worship, [my] heart, in Naṟaiyūr surrounded by fragrant groves,</l>
<l>Before those with crescent-like foreheads no longer have a care for us.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
